Wonderful with this unbeatable room rate! Surprised the hotel is well maintained. Beautiful roof top infinity pool!! Just cross the road and reach my khe beach in 30 seconds. The very low room rate also includes a very good breakfast. Many choices and most of the are delicious! Staff is super nice and welcoming. Love and will definitely return to this hotel!
