Jo F wrote a review Oct 2023
Edmonton, Canada5 contributions4 helpful votes
+1
A La Carte, a wonderful hotel!
A La Carte is situated along the beach. A pedestrian crosswalk separates the hotel and beach. We chose a light studio room which gave us a lot of space. The bed was firm and very comfortable. Every staff member at A La Carte was always helpful and friendly (thank you Victor and your team). There are many restaurants in within walking distance. There’s a lovely Infinity pool with a bar on the 23rd floor. Daily breakfast was a great spread with a lot of choices. Hotel staff are very mindful of guests safety. They called for an attendant to be at the pool when I was the only person swimming in the rain! The hotel isn’t very far from the city centre. We used Grab and is walkable to the Dragon Bridge and Vincom shopping mall.
Dear Guest, Greeting from À La Carte Danang Beach! Thank you for patronizing À La Carte, and taking time out to share your experience on Google. All of us are delighted that we could ensure a comfortable stay during your visit. Thank you once again for your stay and your feedback and look forward to welcoming you back to À La Carte Danang Beach. Have a nice day! À La Carte Team
Curiosity429145 wrote a review Oct 2023
We would recommend this hotel.
The room we were in was wonderful with a great view of the beach across the road. We enjoyed our morning and evening walks on the beach. The bed and the couch were really comfortable. A complimentary breakfast was included which was a buffet filled with both Vietnamese and non Vietnamese food, all of it good. The staff were gracious, available, quick to answer any request. The only drawback, which is not the fault of the hotel, was that every night there was loud, thumping, music playing across the street in a bar until at least midnight. If that would bother you ask for a room facing the other side of the hotel.
Dear Guest, Thank you for the very kind review! It's wonderful to hear that you got great service at our hotel. We look forward to hosting you again soon for another fantastic experience! Have a beautiful day! Best regards, À La Carte Team
