mfjanny L wrote a review Oct 2023
First time of Danang Trip
We stayed for 4 night The hotel was closed to the entrance of the beach,about 15 min to the airport. We enjoyed the infinity swimming pool during night time with good view. breakfast OK. NGO HAN & KIM HUNG were very friendly and helpful. They provided useful information about the sightseeing tour and using the Grab App.
Vader wrote a review Oct 2023
New Delhi, India2 contributions
One of the best beach hotels in Da Nang for sure!
One of the best hotel experiences that I’ve had so far! Will strongly suggest paying extra for the ocean facing room, the view is breathtaking (especially from the higher floors). The beach is super accessible from the hotel and it’s practically a beach resort since you just have to cross the road to reach the beach. The breakfast assortment is also very good.
