Joe S wrote a review Sep 2023
Great trip, great place!
Beautiful pool, bar, room, and breakfast! Overall, very nice place and good location. Be sure to check out the night market if you love seafood, like lobster, shrimp, clams, oysters, and everything else you can think of!
