GrandTour743865 wrote a review Aug 2023
29 contributions8 helpful votes
PERFECT 좋았어!!!
Amazing! Fantastic! Whatever, don't have enough words to compliment that hotel. We are very happy with the stay as the all of them was welcoming & helpful. When I lost my mobile in grab taxi, they found it for me in 3 hours. I can speak in vietanmes only Cảm ơn & Xin chào. Reception staff(both the female and male employees were wearing glasses) and short-haired security staff called the Grab Customer Center in Vietnam to help. Le Chi Van, the security manager tried to find the taxi number and contact grab taxi. When I came back from going out, there was a message in the room that they found my mobile. Finally Mr. Le Chi Van gave it me. Thực sự cảm ơn. We stayed in room #2005. The hotel was very good value. Room is spacious, very clean and comfy. Will definitely be back…
Date of stay: August 2023
